OL,3,CLamine Yamal condemns Spain fans'
OL,4,C'ignorant and racist' anti-Muslim
OL,5,Cchants
OL,7,FSpain's Lamine Yamal has condemned
OL,8,F"ignorant and racist" behaviour after
OL,9,Ffans repeatedly made anti-Muslim
OL,10,Fchants during a game against Egypt.
OL,12,FThe Barcelona winger appeared visibly
OL,13,Fupset by the chanting at the RCDE
OL,14,FStadium in his home city on Tuesday
OL,15,Fnight.
OL,17,FIn a post on Instagram, he said: "I am
OL,18,Fa Muslim. Yesterday in the stadium,
OL,19,Fthe chant 'The one who doesn't jump is
OL,20,FMuslim' was heard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775070658
OL,3,CLamine Yamal condemns Spain fans'
OL,4,C'ignorant and racist' anti-Muslim
OL,5,Cchants
OL,7,F"I know it was aimed at the rival team
OL,8,Fand it wasn't something against me -
OL,9,Fbut as a Muslim, it doesn't stop being
OL,10,Fdisrespectful and something
OL,11,Fintolerable."
OL,13,FThe Spanish football federation (RFEF)
OL,14,Fcondemned the acts, while Catalan
OL,15,Fregional police said they were
OL,16,Finvestigating.
OL,26,@sD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
