OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775070658
OL,3,CLamine Yamal condemns Spain fans'
OL,4,C'ignorant and racist' anti-Muslim
OL,5,Cchants
OL,7,FYamal added: "I understand that not
OL,8,Fall the fans are like that... but to
OL,9,Fthose who sing these things: using a
OL,10,Freligion as a joke in a stadium makes
OL,11,Fyou look like ignorant and racist
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,F"Football is for enjoying it and
OL,15,Fcheering, not for disrespecting people
OL,16,Ffor who they are or what they believe
OL,17,Fin."
OL,19,FSpain's head coach, Luis de la Fuente
OL,20,Falso spoke out against the fans'
OL,21,Fbehaviour.
OL,26,@oD@NOUvD@AOUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
