FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775070658
OL,3,CLamine Yamal condemns Spain fans'
OL,4,C'ignorant and racist' anti-Muslim
OL,5,Cchants
OL,7,F"I feel total and absolute repulsion
OL,8,Ftowards any xenophobic or racist
OL,9,Fattitudes. They are intolerable," de
OL,10,Fla Fuente said after his side's 0-0
OL,11,Fdraw.
OL,13,FFIFA will await reports from officials
OL,14,Fin attendance of the pre-World Cup
OL,15,Ffriendly before deciding whether to
OL,16,Ftake further action.
OL,18,FSpain are due to play Saudi Arabia at
OL,19,Fthe World Cup, and also face Cape
OL,20,FVerde and Uruguay in Group H of the 48-
OL,21,Fteam tournament.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
