OL,5,Cchants
OL,7,FEgypt has games against Belgium, New
OL,8,FZealand and Iran in Group G.
OL,10,FSpain was hosting Egypt for the game,
OL,11,Fwhich was originally set to take place
OL,12,Fin Qatar before the region was
OL,13,Faffected by the Iran war.
